<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; color: #022043;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <strong style="font-size: 20px;"><span style="color: #022043;">Snag</span><span style="color: #FC5A07;">Radar</span></strong>
  </div>

  <h1 style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Please review and sign off your completed work</h1>

  <p style="line-height: 1.6; color: #38506D;">
    The work at <strong><%= @defect.site&.name %></strong><% if @defect.plot %>, <strong><%= @defect.plot.label %></strong><% end %>
    has been marked complete. Have a quick look at the completion photos and confirm you're happy.
  </p>

  <div style="background: #F4F7FB; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 24px 0;">
    <div style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #6B7C93;"><%= @defect.reference || "##{@defect.id}" %></div>
    <div style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 4px;"><%= @defect.title %></div>
  </div>

  <p style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
    <a href="<%= @token_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background: #FC5A07; color: #fff; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 9999px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
      Review &amp; sign off →
    </a>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6B7C93; line-height: 1.6;">
    Your name, signature, IP address and timestamp are stored as evidence the work was approved.
    Link expires in 21 days.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
